data.description: Located within the esteemed guard-gated community of Stallion Mountain, this single-story residence is a true embodiment of elegance and comfort. Spanning 1,925 sq. ft., it was meticulously crafted in 2008, offering 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 well-appointed baths, and a secure 2-car garage. As you enter, you're greeted by a tasteful combination of tile and carpet flooring that flows seamlessly throughout. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is adorned with polished granite countertops and a generous array of cabinetry. The primary bath is a sanctuary with its double sinks, and the luxury of a separate tub and shower. Transitioning outdoors, a serene backyard awaits, featuring a covered patio perfect for relaxation. Residents have the privilege of accessing the renowned 18-hole Stallion Mountain golf course its expansive 38,000 sq. ft. clubhouse. Experience a lifestyle of sophistication and leisure in this remarkable home.
